{"tid":711363,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"用對聯形容香港男人","createTime":"2018-06-21T12:57:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T22:25:22.000Z","uid":55526,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44dd254a84cef83764e28169c7ff6feeeb4a3f5b","tid":711363,"uid":55526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T12:57:14.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;殘燈高牆烙寂影，孤街迷霧吐雲煙。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n想寫香港男人的一生寫照，生活困苦無奈，為香港繁華背後最諷刺的無奈嘆息。<br />\n<br />\n在下綽號&ldquo;對王之王&rdquo;對穿祥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n拋磚，歡迎賜教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6939d7a77d3b741c93b167839c6c6b2f2a730514","tid":711363,"uid":83350,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:17:55.000Z","msg":"「燈光通明人情冷，炒賣投機嘗辣姬。」<br />\n<br />\n前句係講香港現狀，後句帶出香港男士既慾望。"},{"pid":"eec2317d432c46b7256bb930a0b9510ac30811fe","tid":711363,"uid":83350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"「燈<span style=\"color: red;\">火</span>通明人情冷，投機炒賣嘗辣姬。」"},{"pid":"cf411d72e71143294a75ce2043c5e8f6833c26f9","tid":711363,"uid":55526,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"eec2317d432c46b7256bb930a0b9510ac30811fe","tid":711363,"uid":83350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:19:07.000Z","msg":"「燈<span style=\"color: red;\">火</span>通明人情冷，投機炒賣嘗辣姬。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:37:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf09f77f03470578749c1aa43dd33cba8d4ffc0","tid":711363,"uid":145790,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:50:33.000Z","msg":"獨背家累思親雙雙<br />\n困身財散人情涼涼"},{"pid":"eeb4f92e9a6dc7e9c16176a48e294f3adadff2d1","tid":711363,"uid":55526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"caf09f77f03470578749c1aa43dd